Children's dreams come true
The kindergartens and daycare centers in Zollernalbkreis get these days mail.
The Black Bote would like to support in cooperation with Bauhaus and Sparkasse Zollernalb the facilities in the realization of their construction and beautification needs.
Does the nursery a new sandbox?
Participate in the action, all kindergartens, nurseries and creches from the entire Zollernalbkreis.
If you have a construction or beautification desire for your institution, you can apply with this the Black Forest messengers.
Be creative with your kids and amaze the jury of the action Kindergarten site.
A jury consisting of representatives of Black Bote, Bauhaus and Savings Zollernalb, selected from all entries from three wishes.
What are the requirements to participate are there?
The desire should be to realize a building material with a maximum value of 2000 Euro and a (action) day.
In addition, the winner itself must provide for many hard-working construction worker.
What's up with the action and the helpers to?
Bauhaus is supported by the Sparkasse Zollernalb the material available.
It is delivered on the agreed date in the nursery and will be processed directly by the helpers.
Helpers may themselves be parents, grandparents, friends, clubs and of course, the educators and children.
